data.description: ***Property in Default! It must close before 2/20. May need bank approval if offer is below list price*** This fantastic house sits on a spacious .70 ac lot. Nearly all interior surfaces have been tastefully updated with amazing attention to detail + design, including beautiful new flooring, fresh paint throughout, new trim + doors, a gorgeous modern kitchen, with a new hood vent, sink, counters and tile backsplash. A built-in seating nook in the dining area, a revamped entry way, fully updated laundry room and bathrooms, and new lighting + blinds throughout. The stunning kitchen and spacious living-room sit separate from the bedrooms offering a split-level floorplan perfect for entertaining! You will fall in love w/ the details of this home and the new life it has been given! The 4th bedroom is located in the garage w/ its own private bathroom and separate entrance- making it the perfect two-family setup or potential airbnb/ rental for secondary income!
